OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBecoming
OL,6,Fmostly dry and clear through the
OL,7,Fevening and overnight with the chance
OL,8,Fof the odd shower lingering in the
OL,9,Fwest. Occasionally blustery southwest
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FIt will be largely dry with
OL,13,Fbright or sunny spells in the morning.
OL,14,FChance of the odd shower developing in
OL,15,Fthe afternoon. Cooler than recent days.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
