OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith bright spells and light winds for
OL,7,FSaturday. Variable cloud, fresh
OL,8,Fsoutherly winds, and the odd spot of
OL,9,Frain on Sunday and Monday, but plenty
OL,10,Fof dry spells too.
